description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15 Minute Fat Burning HIIT Workout | No Equipment | The Body Coach' from the channel The Body Coach TV by Joe Wicks.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: 3 rounds | 5 exercises | Working for 35 seconds | Rest for 25 seconds

6 High Knees then 4 Lunge Jumps
5 Narrow Press-Ups into 5 wide Press-Ups
5 Toe Touches then 5 Full Body Crunches
6 Mountain Climbers with lateral move
4 Crab Toe Touches then 4 Kick Throughs
